## PDF Operations

### Merge PDFs

**Combine multiple PDFs** into a single document.

**Use cases**:
- Combine invoice sections
- Merge report chapters
- Append attachments to main document

**Pattern**:
1. Provide array of PDF files
2. Gotenberg merges in order
3. Returns combined PDF

### Convert Images to PDF

**Convert images** (PNG, JPEG, TIFF) to PDF.

**Use cases**:
- Scanned documents
- Photo galleries
- Image-based reports

**Pattern**:
1. Upload images
2. Gotenberg creates PDF with one image per page
3. Returns PDF

**Options**:
- Set image quality
- Set page size
- Control image scaling/positioning

### PDF Metadata

**Set PDF metadata** (title, author, subject, keywords).

**Use cases**:
- Document management systems
- Searchability
- Compliance requirements

**Metadata fields**:
- Title
- Author
- Subject
- Keywords
- Creator
- Producer

