## Quick Reference

### Common Operations

| Operation | Use Case | Speed |
|-----------|----------|-------|
| HTML to PDF | Invoices, reports, receipts | Fast (< 1s) |
| URL to PDF | Web pages, dashboards | Medium (2-5s) |
| Office to PDF | DOCX, XLSX, PPTX conversion | Slow (5-15s) |
| Merge PDFs | Combine documents | Fast (< 1s) |
| Images to PDF | Scanned documents | Medium (1-3s) |

